query:
SELECT m.id, m.direction, m.content, m.createdAt, c.customerPhone 
FROM messages m 
JOIN conversations c ON m.conversationId = c.id 
WHERE c.merchantId = 150001 AND m.createdAt > '2025-12-18 07:26:00'
ORDER BY m.createdAt DESC 
LIMIT 10
